task.summary: Version June 1st 2018, Added Shop GUI (Ability to actually play the game now) Fixed Radius Bug (Tower) Edited Waves Added a Wave start button
Version June 1st 2018 #2, Added LaserTower Updated Textures
Version June 1st 2018 #3, Added a bunch more enemies Added Freeze Tower (Still Under Dev) Added Icon
Version June 2nd 2018 #1, Added textures that was missed last commit.
Version June 3rd 2018 #1, Added Freeze Tower Fixed Laser beams, and added freeze beams Fixed bug where the order of enemies was the order of spawned
Version June 3rd 2018 #2, Added Cannon Tower Added Preliminary Sound Effects (Only works one at a time)

Version June 4th 2018 #1, Added Machine Gun Tower Added New Set of Enemies (Pentagons) - excluding White Pentagon Changed reward system, kill to get cash instead of damage to get cash Added new menu buttons Radius now does not show when placed, must be selected to see Ability to sell towers for 1/2 the price bought at Prices and starting money tweaked

Version June 8th 2018 - Major Update!, Added White Pentagon Fixed Numerous Bugs: - Sell button causes a crash if no tower is selected - Able to press the FastForward button quickly and only get half the wave - While a tower is attacking an enemy, and it is sold, the beam stays - Purple pentagons coming out prematurely Added multiple levels, selected randomly when the game is opened Added functionality to the pause button Reduced the damage of the Cannon Tower Tweaked health of the pentagons Updated the documentation of the game (README.md) Reformatted and cleaned up Code Started on comments and documentation

Version June 8th 2018 - Major Update!, Added White Pentagon Fixed Numerous Bugs: - Sell button causes a crash if no tower is selected - Able to press the FastForward button quickly and only get half the wave - While a tower is attacking an enemy, and it is sold, the beam stays - Purple pentagons coming out prematurely Added multiple levels, selected randomly when the game is opened Added functionality to the pause button Tweaked health of the pentagons Reformatted and cleaned up Code Reduced the damage of the Cannon Tower Started on comments and documentation

Version June 11th 2018 - Major Update! Added Game Over screen, and pause screen. Added Heart Tower, and Volley Tower Added new stage, hexagons Modified the waves Added more documentation Updated README.md
